Perlbug README

Short instructions:

    unpack Perlbug.tar.gz
    
    cd ./Perlbug
    
    modify ./config/Configuration
	
    perl Makefile.PL

    make 

    make test 

    make install
    

Long instructions:

    See INSTALL and 'perldoc Perlbug'.

    See also the various help pages/FAQs in the ./text dir.


